    # "After Mei left, I made myself an espresso, which I sipped patiently as I flipped through a large coffee-table book documenting the construction of the new {i}Berliner Philharmonie{/i}."
    ""

# game/after_story.rpy:371
translate german dlc_3_9542e8f6:

